            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1200285</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">机动战士高达系列向来推出都颇受欢迎。Bandai 最新推出的 Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高达头部模型，售 1,299.9 港元，可说非常抵玩，初步上手感觉很有份量，新鲜感一流。事不宜迟，马上开箱评测！</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1200322 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高达头部模型</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">刚推出的 Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高达头部模型，包装盒都几大盒，毕竟也是大大个真人尺寸高达头部模型。打开包装后有 2 个部份，包括 1 份说明书、1 份水贴、由 1 盒发泡胶包装的本体及 1 层配件及 10 cm 高的底座。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1200317 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲水贴</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1200319 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲底座</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200316 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲本体</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>模型大过头，细节位有诚意</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">高达头部模型本体高 37 cm 阔 49 cm 深 33 cm，目测比真人头部的尺寸更大。像真度高，颇忠实地还原元祖高达头部，细节位置绝对有诚意。天线与本体是分开的，跟著说明书安装就可以了，相信难不到高达迷。质感方面，虽然模型大部份是使用了塑料制造，但小编觉得质感不错，有金属感，同时有一定重量。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200323 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模型目测比真人头部的尺寸更大</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200324 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲像真度高，颇忠实地还原元祖高达头部</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200325 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲天线与本体是分开的，跟著说明书安装就可以了</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200345 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200326 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200327 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200329 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲细节位置绝对有诚意，有金属感</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>3 个发光位置，需自行买电池</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">高达头部模型共有 3 个发光位置，分别是 1 对眼及头部前后端监视器。装上电池的步骤很简单，首先打开模型顶部深灰色部份，再用螺丝批开启电池槽，用家要准备 3 粒 AA 电池（模型包装未有提供电池），然后盖上盖子，再启动开关，3 个发光位置就会著灯了。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200330 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲首先打开模型顶部深灰色部份</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200331 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再用螺丝批开启电池槽</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200332 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲准备 3 粒 AA 电池</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200333 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200338 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200339 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200340 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲启动开关，3 个发光位置就会著灯了</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>不建议戴上头上</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">相信很多高达迷都关心模型可否戴上头上，答案是可能可以，但小编不建议。要戴上头上先要拆除所有底部螺丝，但螺丝上得比较实，加上模型里面有电线，而底部空间未必人人都能够通过，基于总总考量，小编一律不建议戴上头上。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200334 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200336 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要戴上头上先要拆除所有底部螺丝，但螺丝上得比较实</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200337 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲底部空间未必人人都能够通过，小编一律不建议戴上头上</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>总结：还原度高，造工细致</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高达头部模型造工精致，几乎所有在影视作品中出现的细节位都有呈现出来，还原度高。著灯部份亦见心思，不只是亮灯，监视器和眼睛里的纹路亦有造好。整体来说 RX 78 2 高达头部模型完成度高，够新鲜感，绝对值得高达迷收藏。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200348 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200341 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200342 aligncenter" src="https://